name: Dean Vincent
description: I am a lover, comforter and a God fearing man. I am full of joy and happiness, I am a man of honor, comfortable, decent and romantic. I am a one woman man and a true lover and admirer. No one is the chosen one but the world of today, we can make each other the chosen one. I am comfortable and I don’t have time for booty calls or one night stands. What you see is what you get, I am not a super star neither am i of high maintenance. If you find me interesting, please feel free to send me a mail and I will be glad to respond with all honesty.
